WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.760 --> 00:00:02.780
Where's Light?

2
00:00:05.790 --> 00:00:06.820
What happened to our son?

3
00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:09.530
Dad. why don't you say something?

4
00:00:09.540 --> 00:00:10.450
Dear!

5
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

6
00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:04.710
"Celebrating LIght's 18th birthday."

7
00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:10.290
"This is a rulebook based on human wisdom"

8
00:01:10.460 --> 00:01:12.770
"which still struggles to answer what justice is."

9
00:01:13.010 --> 00:01:14.160
"Thanks. dad!"

10
00:01:14.650 --> 00:01:16.210
"I want to study it and think about what justice is."

11
00:01:21.900 --> 00:01:24.160
Amane Misa: Surveillance Day 8

12
00:01:24.170 --> 00:01:29.400
Yagami Light: Surveillance Day 3

13
00:01:31.730 --> 00:01:33.040
How is it. Ryuzaki?

14
00:01:34.930 --> 00:01:37.430
Has kira killed anyone yet?

15
00:01:39.630 --> 00:01:43.050
There's no activities so far.

16
00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:46.250
No criminals have been killed.

17
00:01:47.260 --> 00:01:48.440
Is that so...

18
00:01:51.140 --> 00:01:54.170
Then I'm becoming even more suspicious.

19
00:01:55.250 --> 00:01:57.590
I'm soooo bored!

20
00:01:57.990 --> 00:01:59.470
I can't eat apples

21
00:01:59.830 --> 00:02:02.150
and I can't even talk to you.

22
00:02:03.150 --> 00:02:05.490
I wonder how Remu's doing now.

23
00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:45.650
Where's my ID card?

24
00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:47.920
Does anyone know?

25
00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:29.380
Don't make a sound!

26
00:03:29.900 --> 00:03:32.540
I brought a little gift for you.

27
00:03:35.900 --> 00:03:37.030
Misa. Day 12
Light: Day 7

28
00:03:37.210 --> 00:03:39.060
I want to see Light!

29
00:03:40.970 --> 00:03:45.120
I want to see Light. stalkers!

30
00:03:47.050 --> 00:03:47.930
Light.

31
00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:50.150
You look exhausted.

32
00:03:52.490 --> 00:03:53.640
Are you okay?

33
00:03:56.220 --> 00:03:58.460
Yeah. I know. I look so miserable right now.

34
00:04:00.180 --> 00:04:02.810
But I don't care about such as useless pride...

35
00:04:04.950 --> 00:04:05.690
"I discard it!"

36
00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:09.210
You "discard" it?

37
00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:12.000
You'll lose your memory...

38
00:04:12.870 --> 00:04:14.400
Alright. Light.

39
00:04:15.700 --> 00:04:16.410
Goodbye.

40
00:04:39.920 --> 00:04:40.720
Ryuzaki...

41
00:04:42.530 --> 00:04:43.410
What's wrong?

42
00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:48.150
I know I asked you to do this to me...

43
00:04:49.470 --> 00:04:50.950
But now I surely know...

44
00:04:53.040 --> 00:04:54.630
This is a waste of time.

45
00:04:55.940 --> 00:04:57.300
I'm not Kira!

46
00:04:58.170 --> 00:05:01.490
I'll be the judge of that. not you!

47
00:05:02.170 --> 00:05:04.440
It's totally impossible to do such cruel things

48
00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:06.370
without being conscious...

49
00:05:07.580 --> 00:05:09.150
Don't you think so?

50
00:05:09.740 --> 00:05:12.150
It was you who said that you might be Kira

51
00:05:13.270 --> 00:05:14.880
without being conscious.

52
00:05:15.530 --> 00:05:17.310
While I'm here. I clearly saw my goal...

53
00:05:18.060 --> 00:05:20.520
I won't let Kira go free. he drove me into a corner.

54
00:05:21.450 --> 00:05:22.340
Ryuzaki!

55
00:05:23.050 --> 00:05:25.140
Let's cooperate and find a way to reach Kira!

56
00:05:26.070 --> 00:05:29.760
We can get him!

57
00:05:30.820 --> 00:05:34.230
Light...
suddenly became so positive.

58
00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:53.640
Misa: Day 19
Light: Day 14

59
00:05:54.130 --> 00:05:56.630
Since he offered to do it. but

60
00:05:57.740 --> 00:05:58.890
I'm worried about Misa.

61
00:06:04.030 --> 00:06:05.210
She's a tough kid!

62
00:06:05.990 --> 00:06:07.490
If I were her. I'd go insane!

63
00:06:15.090 --> 00:06:15.700
Ryuzaki!

64
00:06:17.430 --> 00:06:18.470
Kira is back!

65
00:06:19.780 --> 00:06:21.720
Criminals are dying of heart attack one after another!

66
00:06:24.430 --> 00:06:25.190
Light!

67
00:06:25.990 --> 00:06:29.070
There's been no action from Kira for 2 weeks.

68
00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:31.370
It's time for you to admit that you're Kira.

69
00:06:31.370 --> 00:06:31.970
Hey!

70
00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:37.130
If you see only the current situation. I'm guilty. But this is a trap...

71
00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:41.880
I said I'm not Kira!
Believe me!

72
00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:08.950
Why did Kira... choose me as his replacement?

73
00:07:09.730 --> 00:07:13.720
You often predicted who'll be the next target of Kira.

74
00:07:14.390 --> 00:07:17.690
You must have noticed the reason through your reports.

75
00:07:25.990 --> 00:07:27.300
Kira's punishment...

76
00:07:27.540 --> 00:07:30.530
...is nearly the same as my view on justice.

77
00:07:31.230 --> 00:07:32.320
That's what I thought!

78
00:07:39.630 --> 00:07:42.340
Kira is just trying to make the world a better place.

79
00:07:42.540 --> 00:07:45.860
It's my mission to tell the people that he's doing the right thing.

80
00:07:47.190 --> 00:07:49.750
If I were Kira. I would use the media more efficiently!

81
00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:55.860
That makes you the most suitable person as Kira's partner.

82
00:07:56.490 --> 00:07:57.690
That is the reason

83
00:07:58.730 --> 00:08:00.650
Kira chose me as his partner...

84
00:08:11.210 --> 00:08:16.070
Misa: Day 23
Light: Day 18

85
00:08:18.630 --> 00:08:22.520
Criminals are constantly being killed.

86
00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:25.510
Even the ones they never knew.

87
00:08:25.840 --> 00:08:29.400
It's impossible to kill them in this situation...

88
00:08:33.180 --> 00:08:33.980
For example.

89
00:08:34.730 --> 00:08:36.580
if Kira's ability has been transferred to another person

90
00:08:37.300 --> 00:08:39.430
and the person has become the Third Kira

91
00:08:39.990 --> 00:08:42.450
and they've lost their memories...

92
00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:44.150
It explains everything!

93
00:08:45.030 --> 00:08:46.100
Even if you were right.

94
00:08:46.710 --> 00:08:48.180
there's no way to prove it.

95
00:08:54.040 --> 00:08:54.820
Ryuzaki!

96
00:08:58.130 --> 00:09:00.740
Why don't we try a different approach?

97
00:09:17.450 --> 00:09:19.390
How do you feel?

98
00:09:22.580 --> 00:09:23.520
Good. thanks!

99
00:09:24.820 --> 00:09:26.700
I'm impressed with your courage...

100
00:09:28.910 --> 00:09:31.960
Still. we have the evidence found in Amane's room.

101
00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:36.950
You can't go outside until we solve the case.

102
00:09:37.870 --> 00:09:39.520
If I have to stay here anyway

103
00:09:40.410 --> 00:09:43.300
then let me go back to the team and help you find Kira.

104
00:09:43.940 --> 00:09:47.210
Yes. I was thinking about the exact same thing.

105
00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:53.350
You have to stay with me all day and assist me.

106
00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:55.970
Thanks. Ryuzaki!

107
00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.770
Let's find Kira together.

108
00:10:07.250 --> 00:10:08.630
I love you...

109
00:10:09.950 --> 00:10:11.030
Light!

110
00:10:25.730 --> 00:10:27.600
Mrs. Wakita!
Are you okay?

111
00:10:27.700 --> 00:10:28.680
What happened to you?

112
00:10:29.030 --> 00:10:30.060
Get an ambulance!

113
00:10:36.950 --> 00:10:38.130
She's dead!

114
00:10:39.170 --> 00:10:42.560
Her name is Wakita Masako and she was wanted for

115
00:10:42.820 --> 00:10:45.400
killing her colleague when she was working in a nightclub.

116
00:10:46.290 --> 00:10:47.410
Is this another case

117
00:10:48.050 --> 00:10:50.140
of punishment from Kira?

118
00:10:50.930 --> 00:10:56.870
We found Wakita's address and tried to interview her.

119
00:10:57.070 --> 00:10:58.860
but she died in front of us.

120
00:10:59.540 --> 00:11:02.020
Mrs. Takada. you must be shocked!

121
00:11:03.100 --> 00:11:05.040
She did not have any health problem

122
00:11:05.300 --> 00:11:08.670
so it is natural to think that she was killed by Kira.

123
00:11:10.210 --> 00:11:12.070
Now please look at this graph.

124
00:11:13.150 --> 00:11:16.140
This is the result of a poll taken from 1000 people in Japan.

125
00:11:16.830 --> 00:11:17.650
According to the result.

126
00:11:17.820 --> 00:11:21.200
60% of them are supporting Kira...

127
00:11:21.290 --> 00:11:22.680
This is surprising isn't it?

128
00:11:22.950 --> 00:11:23.870
I don't think so.

129
00:11:24.820 --> 00:11:29.250
Considering that the crime rate has been decreasing

130
00:11:29.530 --> 00:11:31.680
by the appearance of Kira. this result is expected.

131
00:11:34.700 --> 00:11:36.430
Not bad!

132
00:11:38.490 --> 00:11:41.260
This is a fact that Kira is fighting against evil

133
00:11:42.480 --> 00:11:44.650
What is the true justice?

134
00:11:45.620 --> 00:11:47.770
Does the police. or L. really can help us?

135
00:11:48.580 --> 00:11:50.320
Kira is trying to make us thing.

136
00:11:51.070 --> 00:11:52.700
She's good!

137
00:11:54.780 --> 00:11:56.660
We can't blame her. because

138
00:11:57.990 --> 00:12:01.300
we haven't found any clues to go on.

139
00:12:02.700 --> 00:12:04.590
What's wrong Ryuzaki?
It's not like you.

140
00:12:06.260 --> 00:12:09.350
Oh. great work!

141
00:12:09.730 --> 00:12:10.750
Thank you for supervising!

142
00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:12.970
Your comments were witty.

143
00:12:14.620 --> 00:12:15.620
Thank you so much!

144
00:12:16.670 --> 00:12:18.010
The director said that...

145
00:12:18.930 --> 00:12:20.700
you'd be a good anchor.

146
00:12:21.440 --> 00:12:21.910
Really?

147
00:12:22.940 --> 00:12:25.390
for being critical towards the society through Kira's case...

148
00:12:26.320 --> 00:12:29.230
Your brave. intelligent attitude has attracted the viewers.

149
00:12:31.210 --> 00:12:33.050
You're becoming more attractive.

150
00:12:34.440 --> 00:12:35.270
Mr. Demegawa!

151
00:12:38.620 --> 00:12:40.740
Could you ask your boss

152
00:12:41.740 --> 00:12:43.990
to spray pesticide in the studio

153
00:12:44.410 --> 00:12:46.730
since a noisy bug's flying around here?

154
00:12:47.280 --> 00:12:48.520
Saeko!

155
00:12:49.090 --> 00:12:50.090
Let's go have dinner?

156
00:12:52.850 --> 00:12:53.740
Kiyomi!

157
00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:56.410
You know. each employee has an appropriate role. right?

158
00:12:56.970 --> 00:12:58.130
What is your role. then?

159
00:12:59.490 --> 00:13:01.590
No one's listening to your trashy comments!

160
00:13:02.610 --> 00:13:03.550
Let's go!

161
00:13:10.070 --> 00:13:13.910
I say she's too ugly to be the anchor for our show!

162
00:13:14.340 --> 00:13:15.450
Oh. come on!

163
00:13:15.940 --> 00:13:18.810
We employees can't say no to your boss. you know.

164
00:13:19.440 --> 00:13:20.510
Are you kidding me?

165
00:13:20.940 --> 00:13:23.570
You're the one who said no to your boss and showed Kira's video!

166
00:13:24.750 --> 00:13:26.220
You slept with her. didn't you?

167
00:13:27.400 --> 00:13:30.580
There's nobody but you who got a job by sleeping with me.

168
00:13:32.950 --> 00:13:33.550
Stop the car!

169
00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:34.740
Huh?

170
00:13:35.270 --> 00:13:36.380
Stop the car now!

171
00:13:45.470 --> 00:13:46.870
I'll never forgive her!

172
00:13:47.990 --> 00:13:48.890
Hey. wait!

173
00:13:49.670 --> 00:13:50.650
Calm down!

174
00:13:52.310 --> 00:13:53.350
What's the matter with you!

175
00:13:57.560 --> 00:13:59.480
You can't catch a taxi here!

176
00:14:19.910 --> 00:14:20.560
Good evening!

177
00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:24.540
Welcome to Evening Spot.
I'm Takada Kiyomi. the new anchor

178
00:14:26.490 --> 00:14:27.460
First of all.

179
00:14:28.280 --> 00:14:30.830
I have to announce some sad news...

180
00:14:32.570 --> 00:14:36.080
Last night. Nishiyama Saeko. our excellent former anchor.

181
00:14:36.560 --> 00:14:38.270
died of a car accident.

182
00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:41.500
For me she was...

183
00:14:42.910 --> 00:14:44.360
a few years senior to me

184
00:14:44.910 --> 00:14:48.390
and one of the persons I respected the most.

185
00:14:50.530 --> 00:14:52.610
It is very sad that...

186
00:14:53.880 --> 00:14:56.470
my first job as an anchor is

187
00:14:58.320 --> 00:14:59.520
to announce Saeko's death.

188
00:15:04.350 --> 00:15:06.950
This feels like being on a honeymoon!

189
00:15:08.960 --> 00:15:11.960
If I can always spend my time with you like this

190
00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:13.810
I won't want to go back to work.

191
00:15:16.830 --> 00:15:22.260
...But if they lock me up again. I'll die!

192
00:15:23.700 --> 00:15:24.490
Oh. sorry!

193
00:15:29.120 --> 00:15:30.180
Light!

194
00:15:30.830 --> 00:15:31.720
Are you studying?

195
00:15:31.840 --> 00:15:34.200
Sorry Misa. can you please leave me alone for a while?

196
00:15:52.590 --> 00:15:53.610
I'll go downstairs.

197
00:15:54.390 --> 00:15:55.460
Don't leave me alone!

198
00:16:01.550 --> 00:16:03.520
Light! Come back soon. okay?

199
00:16:03.970 --> 00:16:06.980
I'm sorry. but I'll set you free soon.

200
00:16:21.260 --> 00:16:23.430
Ryuzaki is a little depressed.

201
00:16:23.870 --> 00:16:26.500
Yeah. because he lost all of his clues...

202
00:16:28.600 --> 00:16:30.030
You're too loud!

203
00:16:30.490 --> 00:16:31.300
Ryuzaki!

204
00:16:31.830 --> 00:16:33.070
Please be honest!

205
00:16:33.590 --> 00:16:35.730
What is the percentage that I'm Kira?

206
00:16:37.170 --> 00:16:40.210
The percentage that you are Kira is...

207
00:16:40.840 --> 00:16:41.940
almost zero.

208
00:16:42.790 --> 00:16:43.440
I see...

209
00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:45.700
Great!

210
00:16:46.320 --> 00:16:47.370
I'm so happy!

211
00:16:48.130 --> 00:16:52.040
I'm also happy that you don't seem to be Kira. but

212
00:16:53.270 --> 00:16:55.660
at the same time I lost all the clues...

213
00:16:56.870 --> 00:16:58.620
There's a vital clue.

214
00:16:59.660 --> 00:17:00.400
What if I said so?

215
00:17:01.950 --> 00:17:03.850
When will you come back?

216
00:17:04.260 --> 00:17:05.200
Are you serious?

217
00:17:05.970 --> 00:17:06.670
Look at this!

218
00:17:11.080 --> 00:17:13.970
The red one is Kira's action before I was confined

219
00:17:14.590 --> 00:17:16.920
and the blue one is his new action.

220
00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:18.720
I profiled them statistically.

221
00:17:19.360 --> 00:17:22.150
Can it be the same person?

222
00:17:22.260 --> 00:17:22.940
No.

223
00:17:23.520 --> 00:17:25.080
They have some differences...

224
00:17:31.250 --> 00:17:32.540
Oh. they really do!

225
00:17:34.110 --> 00:17:37.130
Even if you try to imitate someone's movement

226
00:17:37.190 --> 00:17:39.300
you can't hide your habits or personality.

227
00:17:39.850 --> 00:17:42.450
They appear to be a remarkable tendency...

228
00:17:43.340 --> 00:17:44.160
Ryuzaki.

229
00:17:44.630 --> 00:17:46.180
He's got the energy again!

230
00:17:46.490 --> 00:17:47.560
I bet you know it.

231
00:17:48.350 --> 00:17:51.310
If Kira before and after the restraint was the same person...

232
00:17:51.340 --> 00:17:53.560
then the distribution wouldn't be so different.

233
00:17:54.780 --> 00:17:56.970
It means that it is a different person and

234
00:17:56.970 --> 00:17:59.720
we can see the distinct characteristics that show their tendencies.

235
00:18:01.260 --> 00:18:02.270
How is it. Ryuzaki?

236
00:18:02.900 --> 00:18:03.830
Doesn't it give you some motivation?

237
00:18:04.940 --> 00:18:06.660
Yes. Light. thank you.

238
00:18:08.210 --> 00:18:09.520
By the way. what are the characteristics?

239
00:18:10.900 --> 00:18:13.550
Well. the first characteristic is publicity.

240
00:18:14.050 --> 00:18:18.750
I mean. the new Kira cares slightly more about cases featured by the media.

241
00:18:19.330 --> 00:18:21.070
And the second factor is...

242
00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:22.470
gender.

243
00:18:22.990 --> 00:18:27.450
The new one focuses on more cases related to women.

244
00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:29.910
This Kira may be a woman.

245
00:18:30.610 --> 00:18:32.360
And the third factor is...

246
00:18:33.600 --> 00:18:36.060
which might already be the answer...

247
00:18:36.490 --> 00:18:37.950
What? Oh come on. Light. tell us!

248
00:18:38.310 --> 00:18:41.580
frequency of the cases reported by one broadcasting company.

249
00:18:42.310 --> 00:18:44.010
Which company?

250
00:18:45.520 --> 00:18:46.170
It's Sakura TV.

251
00:18:49.780 --> 00:18:51.230
To sum up...

252
00:18:52.560 --> 00:18:55.260
compared to the First Kira. this new Kira is

253
00:18:55.930 --> 00:19:01.040
more media-oriented. feminine. and in Sakura TV.

254
00:19:03.810 --> 00:19:06.410
The anchor died of accident and the new one is female!

255
00:20:14.400 --> 00:20:17.120
Does she keep a diary in such an old notebook?

256
00:20:18.320 --> 00:20:19.780
That's not what snobbish people do.

257
00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:21.570
She must have a lot of money.

258
00:20:22.130 --> 00:20:25.750
I don't think it's a diary. She's copying down from the PC screen.

259
00:20:26.970 --> 00:20:28.890
Can you zoom in the surface of the notebook?

260
00:20:29.480 --> 00:20:30.750
Okay. wait a second...

261
00:20:42.410 --> 00:20:43.350
What are these?

262
00:20:44.920 --> 00:20:48.720
Names of the criminals who've just been killed by Kira.

263
00:20:49.220 --> 00:20:53.310
Mrs. Sagami. capture them and confirm that they are.

264
00:20:53.850 --> 00:20:54.760
Yes!

265
00:20:57.610 --> 00:21:00.550
Killing one after another everyday...

266
00:21:00.930 --> 00:21:03.690
Are there anybody left to kill?

267
00:21:04.220 --> 00:21:06.640
It tells you how sinful human beings are...

268
00:21:07.840 --> 00:21:10.530
Look who's talking!

269
00:21:10.560 --> 00:21:11.550
I know...

270
00:21:12.550 --> 00:21:14.890
Punishing the sinful people makes me even more sinful...

271
00:21:15.970 --> 00:21:17.480
But even if those sins burden me for my entire life

272
00:21:18.440 --> 00:21:20.380
I have to fulfill my duty.

273
00:21:21.030 --> 00:21:22.400
Is she talking to herself?

274
00:21:22.610 --> 00:21:23.160
No...

275
00:21:23.850 --> 00:21:25.290
She's definitely talking to someone else.

276
00:21:31.300 --> 00:21:32.530
It's confirmed!

277
00:21:33.580 --> 00:21:35.870
Names on the left page belong to the criminals

278
00:21:36.210 --> 00:21:39.030
who died of heart attack yesterday.

279
00:21:39.810 --> 00:21:43.920
Accurate details of when and how they died including the unannounced cases.

280
00:21:44.560 --> 00:21:45.960
We got it!

281
00:21:46.510 --> 00:21:48.470
Boss! Let me arrest her!

282
00:21:48.610 --> 00:21:51.880
She can make an excuse that she was just researching their deaths.

283
00:21:53.130 --> 00:21:54.100
You're right...

284
00:21:54.160 --> 00:21:54.990
One more thing...

285
00:21:56.000 --> 00:21:59.220
What she's writing down on the right page now

286
00:21:59.650 --> 00:22:01.290
are also names of the criminals.

287
00:22:02.070 --> 00:22:04.080
but they are still alive.

288
00:22:06.190 --> 00:22:08.570
They must be the next targets.

289
00:22:09.900 --> 00:22:12.510
If they really die tomorrow. we can conclude that she's Kira

290
00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:17.090
or she has some kind of relation to Kira.

291
00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:19.420
We can't just wait until those people die!

292
00:22:20.480 --> 00:22:22.290
Damn it. what should we do!

293
00:22:22.690 --> 00:22:24.210
We can use Kira's cruelty.

294
00:22:27.480 --> 00:22:28.690
Hello. Mrs. Takada!

295
00:22:29.890 --> 00:22:33.570
You keep getting scoops about Kira as a supporter.

296
00:22:34.890 --> 00:22:37.580
I found out the reasons...

297
00:22:37.870 --> 00:22:38.940
What do you mean?

298
00:22:40.010 --> 00:22:42.150
I peeked in your room.

299
00:22:43.720 --> 00:22:44.970
It's illegal!

300
00:22:45.310 --> 00:22:48.530
Every secret is hidden in your black notebook. right?

301
00:22:49.090 --> 00:22:50.860
I want you to buy the tapes

302
00:22:51.530 --> 00:22:52.590
for 5 million yen.

303
00:23:33.620 --> 00:23:35.630
All the names she wrote down yesterday...

304
00:23:36.010 --> 00:23:37.710
match the criminals who died today.

305
00:23:38.370 --> 00:23:39.920
Takada Kiyomi is Kira!

306
00:23:40.700 --> 00:23:41.270
She definitely is!

307
00:23:52.390 --> 00:23:53.340
I'm the one who called you...

308
00:23:59.490 --> 00:24:01.430
"Miatsuo Yosuke"

309
00:24:02.100 --> 00:24:06.080
If I die. the tapes will automatically go public.

310
00:24:06.770 --> 00:24:09.610
Are you doing this with someone else?

311
00:24:09.660 --> 00:24:10.620
No. I'm alone.

312
00:24:14.030 --> 00:24:16.460
There's my account number on the back of the card.

313
00:24:17.380 --> 00:24:20.230
Transfer 5 million yen to my account.

314
00:24:21.490 --> 00:24:23.230
Once payment is confirmed

315
00:24:23.750 --> 00:24:24.950
I'll give you the tapes.

316
00:24:26.250 --> 00:24:27.350
Thank you!

317
00:24:33.950 --> 00:24:36.530
It's me. Kiyomi. Turn on the TV!

318
00:24:36.790 --> 00:24:37.520
Sakura TV.

319
00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:39.310
Why?

320
00:24:39.810 --> 00:24:40.820
No reason. just turn on the TV!

321
00:24:47.440 --> 00:24:49.610
Kira is a woman?

322
00:24:50.580 --> 00:24:53.050
Wow. I couldn't think of it...

323
00:24:53.080 --> 00:24:54.240
"Special Program: Chasing Kira's Identity"

324
00:24:54.270 --> 00:24:56.770
I have the tapes as evidence.

325
00:24:57.780 --> 00:24:59.370
Wait. It's too soon to show them!

326
00:25:00.090 --> 00:25:03.000
We'll show you the videos at the end of the program.

327
00:25:04.440 --> 00:25:05.810
You'll see Kira's identity.

328
00:25:06.130 --> 00:25:09.640
1 hour 25 minutes and 40 seconds left...

329
00:25:10.520 --> 00:25:12.850
until then. we'll ask our guests some more questions.

330
00:25:12.850 --> 00:25:14.480
We were scooped by other guys.

331
00:25:16.070 --> 00:25:18.370
I'm sorry...
I'll call you back.

332
00:25:19.310 --> 00:25:20.390
"that female..."

333
00:25:24.290 --> 00:25:25.010
I did as you said.

334
00:25:26.190 --> 00:25:27.590
You're a good actor!

335
00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:37.160
Now. what do we do next?

336
00:25:43.030 --> 00:25:45.920
"Matsuo Yosuke's suicide"

337
00:25:47.020 --> 00:25:48.870
22:36. refuses to appear on the program.

338
00:25:51.440 --> 00:25:55.040
After cleaning out all the evidences he has

339
00:25:56.100 --> 00:25:57.840
he jumps from the roof of the building.

340
00:26:01.050 --> 00:26:02.720
She's writing down how he's going to die.

341
00:26:03.520 --> 00:26:06.270
Kira can control the action of the people she's going to kill!

342
00:26:08.350 --> 00:26:09.970
It's safe. Remu!

343
00:26:11.070 --> 00:26:12.530
"Now it's safe"...

344
00:26:13.980 --> 00:26:15.060
What is she talking about?

345
00:26:15.870 --> 00:26:21.460
Does she really believe that Matsuda will act according to what she's written?

346
00:26:25.860 --> 00:26:29.950
Are you for or against Kira's actions?

347
00:26:30.480 --> 00:26:31.410
Don't you see?

348
00:26:32.170 --> 00:26:35.020
If I supported Kira. I wouldn't appear on TV like this.

349
00:26:36.170 --> 00:26:37.470
Don't you think it's dangerous?

350
00:26:37.500 --> 00:26:38.760
It's a minute past the time....

351
00:26:39.260 --> 00:26:40.520
Remu. what's going on?

352
00:26:41.870 --> 00:26:42.610
"Remu"...

353
00:26:44.200 --> 00:26:45.540
What is "Remu"?

354
00:26:45.890 --> 00:26:46.750
Who is she talking to?

355
00:26:50.610 --> 00:26:51.640
A Shinigami?

356
00:26:54.550 --> 00:26:58.360
"Matsuo Yosuke"...
It must be a false name!

357
00:26:58.910 --> 00:27:01.250
Remu! You must've known it since you're a Shinigami!

358
00:27:01.970 --> 00:27:03.100
You didn't tell me!

359
00:27:04.210 --> 00:27:07.840
She often says "Shinigami".

360
00:27:08.070 --> 00:27:09.360
Is it a code or something?

361
00:27:10.590 --> 00:27:13.250
The most logical way is to think that

362
00:27:14.030 --> 00:27:15.420
Shinigami exist.

363
00:27:16.560 --> 00:27:17.060
What?

364
00:27:18.130 --> 00:27:19.010
Okay....

365
00:27:20.070 --> 00:27:20.850
Let's make a deal.

366
00:27:22.030 --> 00:27:23.400
Give me the Shinigami's eyes!

367
00:27:28.660 --> 00:27:30.340
The Shinigami's eyes?

368
00:27:34.000 --> 00:27:35.550
The Second Kira said the same thing.

369
00:27:37.510 --> 00:27:39.090
The Second Kira has the ability to kill only by seeing the faces.

370
00:27:40.880 --> 00:27:42.340
That's "the Shinigami's eyes".

371
00:28:56.300 --> 00:28:56.940
Roll down the window.

372
00:29:02.690 --> 00:29:03.510
Show me your ID.

373
00:29:05.710 --> 00:29:06.520
You don't have it?

374
00:29:08.340 --> 00:29:10.990
Don't look at me like that. rules are rules.

375
00:29:12.940 --> 00:29:14.550
Shidohara Genta.

376
00:29:16.610 --> 00:29:17.920
How did you know my name?

377
00:29:21.880 --> 00:29:22.570
Wait!

378
00:29:23.570 --> 00:29:25.680
Do you appear on TV?

379
00:29:26.830 --> 00:29:28.910
Something TV...

380
00:29:29.660 --> 00:29:31.040
You're an anchor. right?

381
00:29:32.380 --> 00:29:33.310
What are you doing?

382
00:29:33.760 --> 00:29:34.480
Wait!

383
00:30:09.180 --> 00:30:12.290
A policeman fell down. but I can't help him!

384
00:30:12.650 --> 00:30:13.550
Got it

385
00:30:13.840 --> 00:30:15.700
Did she use "the eyes"?

386
00:30:16.670 --> 00:30:18.570
It's too dangerous to let her go any further.

387
00:30:19.540 --> 00:30:24.000
We don't know how she did it. but it's better to catch her

388
00:31:16.360 --> 00:31:17.710
Freeze!

389
00:31:24.150 --> 00:31:25.240
Let me go!

390
00:31:39.110 --> 00:31:40.340
Let me go!

391
00:31:47.810 --> 00:31:51.350
We have watched every single action you made!

392
00:31:53.610 --> 00:31:55.860
The TV program was a fake!

393
00:31:57.240 --> 00:31:58.260
It was a trap!

394
00:31:58.820 --> 00:31:59.810
Takada Kiyomi!

395
00:32:01.380 --> 00:32:03.190
How did you do that?

396
00:32:04.820 --> 00:32:05.910
Are you a detective?

397
00:32:06.050 --> 00:32:06.960
As Kira...

398
00:32:07.500 --> 00:32:09.270
How did you kill those people?

399
00:32:11.830 --> 00:32:13.550
You wrote the names in the notebook...

400
00:32:18.630 --> 00:32:21.200
After writing them down... what did you do?

401
00:32:23.350 --> 00:32:24.370
I just write them down.

402
00:32:24.740 --> 00:32:26.560
I asked what you did after that!

403
00:32:28.550 --> 00:32:29.870
Why don't you try it yourself?

404
00:32:35.700 --> 00:32:38.020
You write names down and...

405
00:32:38.190 --> 00:32:39.550
the person whose name is written dies.

406
00:32:40.220 --> 00:32:41.520
The notebook of the Shinigami.

407
00:32:54.930 --> 00:32:57.060
What the...?!

408
00:32:59.120 --> 00:33:00.180
Dad. what's wrong?

409
00:33:09.780 --> 00:33:12.740
When you touch it. you can see the Shinigami?

410
00:33:20.480 --> 00:33:22.530
Ryuzaki. let me touch it!

411
00:33:38.850 --> 00:33:41.380
Light... are you okay?

412
00:33:43.020 --> 00:33:43.790
Yeah!

413
00:33:49.550 --> 00:33:50.410
I won!

414
00:33:51.730 --> 00:33:53.090
Everything's under control!

415
00:33:56.840 --> 00:34:01.230
If I touch the Death Note. my memories will come back.

416
00:34:01.830 --> 00:34:02.750
Is this really true?

417
00:34:03.430 --> 00:34:04.390
Yes. but

418
00:34:04.430 --> 00:34:08.190
you can only remember when you touch the Death Note

419
00:34:08.280 --> 00:34:11.750
if the Note wasn't the one you used before.

420
00:34:12.130 --> 00:34:16.300
But if I keep the ownership. the memory won't be lost right?

421
00:34:18.200 --> 00:34:19.240
How can I get the ownership?

422
00:34:19.900 --> 00:34:23.950
While you have the memories. kill the former owner.

423
00:34:24.690 --> 00:34:27.730
Good.
That explanation is enough.

424
00:34:28.510 --> 00:34:29.030
Remu!

425
00:34:29.660 --> 00:34:31.650
Give this to the Third Kira.

426
00:34:32.530 --> 00:34:35.050
If you're a Shinigami. you can find a suitable one.

427
00:34:35.700 --> 00:34:39.670
And after 13 days. let that person resume Kira's job.

428
00:34:40.220 --> 00:34:41.820
I can choose anyone?

429
00:34:42.730 --> 00:34:47.400
As you won't remember. you can't reach the new owner.

430
00:34:47.950 --> 00:34:50.960
I know about my ability more than anyone else.

431
00:34:52.060 --> 00:34:55.010
I will definitely try hard to find the new Kira...

432
00:34:55.440 --> 00:34:56.350
and catch the person!

433
00:34:57.460 --> 00:35:01.190
I'll touch the Note before L. or at the same time

434
00:35:02.920 --> 00:35:04.000
And one more thing...

435
00:35:05.260 --> 00:35:07.330
I have something I want you to write down in the Note.

436
00:35:08.400 --> 00:35:09.210
What is it?

437
00:35:11.100 --> 00:35:12.170
I've made up

438
00:35:13.790 --> 00:35:15.390
a false rule of the Death Note.

439
00:35:28.790 --> 00:35:30.410
Shinigami exist.

440
00:35:30.530 --> 00:35:31.610
That explains everything.

441
00:35:31.960 --> 00:35:34.540
Now I know how they kill.

442
00:35:35.410 --> 00:35:37.300
If you write down a person's name on the notebook

443
00:35:37.740 --> 00:35:39.720
that person dies!

444
00:35:40.660 --> 00:35:42.210
Is this correct. Takada Kiyomi?

445
00:35:45.040 --> 00:35:48.050
The Shinigami...
The killer notebook...

446
00:35:49.020 --> 00:35:51.430
Who will believe this?

447
00:35:52.510 --> 00:35:55.400
We can't try her with the current laws!

448
00:35:55.850 --> 00:35:56.760
That's right!

449
00:35:57.290 --> 00:35:59.010
I didn't kill anybody!

450
00:35:59.980 --> 00:36:01.630
I just wrote down the names.

451
00:36:02.400 --> 00:36:02.800
No.

452
00:36:04.040 --> 00:36:06.660
If we can prove that the notebook kills people...

453
00:36:07.340 --> 00:36:08.670
You'll be guilty.

454
00:36:09.450 --> 00:36:10.420
Death Penalty.

455
00:36:18.410 --> 00:36:21.020
Humans. listen!

456
00:36:21.540 --> 00:36:23.980
I'm a Shinigami. Remu.

457
00:36:24.800 --> 00:36:27.800
Only the humans who touched the Death Note can see me.

458
00:36:28.050 --> 00:36:30.810
I can see your lifespan.

459
00:36:31.710 --> 00:36:35.080
And I can take your lives away.

460
00:36:36.010 --> 00:36:39.730
So you'd better not make me angry!

461
00:36:41.680 --> 00:36:45.000
The Death Note has the power of the Shinigami.

462
00:36:46.190 --> 00:36:47.860
That woman is correct!

463
00:36:48.410 --> 00:36:52.150
The human whose name is written on the Death Note shall die!

464
00:36:52.460 --> 00:36:54.110
"Takada Kiyomi"

465
00:36:54.390 --> 00:36:58.690
With the so-called Death Note you can control the dying situations. can't you?

466
00:37:01.140 --> 00:37:03.430
Why don't you try it yourself

467
00:37:04.050 --> 00:37:06.370
by writing her name on the Note?

468
00:37:07.280 --> 00:37:08.770
Remu. what do you...

469
00:37:28.810 --> 00:37:29.460
Takada!

470
00:37:37.750 --> 00:37:38.560
She's dead...

471
00:37:42.940 --> 00:37:44.870
Light. hand me the notebook!

472
00:38:03.720 --> 00:38:04.760
Overall.

473
00:38:05.180 --> 00:38:07.630
Why did Takada Kiyomi die?

474
00:38:08.350 --> 00:38:10.780
Accidental heart attack or...

475
00:38:10.910 --> 00:38:12.250
suicide?

476
00:38:13.540 --> 00:38:14.860
Killed by the other Kira?

477
00:38:16.330 --> 00:38:17.770
What do you think. Shinigami?

478
00:38:18.810 --> 00:38:20.130
Don't ask me.

479
00:38:23.450 --> 00:38:26.900
The name on the notebook and the dead criminals are the same. but

480
00:38:27.190 --> 00:38:29.200
there's no name before Light's confinement.

481
00:38:31.380 --> 00:38:32.430
What do you think?

482
00:38:32.770 --> 00:38:37.180
The owner of the Note might die when the ownership moves to another person.

483
00:38:38.060 --> 00:38:40.020
The First and the Second Kira might have already...

484
00:38:41.100 --> 00:38:42.980
I see. Now Takada has died

485
00:38:43.910 --> 00:38:46.510
and the ownership of this notebook was transferred to someone else.

486
00:38:47.220 --> 00:38:48.470
What do you think. Shinigami?

487
00:38:49.470 --> 00:38:50.490
Don't ask me.

488
00:38:51.680 --> 00:38:53.890
Who owns the Note now?

489
00:38:54.640 --> 00:38:55.790
I cannot answer.

490
00:38:56.930 --> 00:38:59.230
Is that the only thing you can say?

491
00:39:00.240 --> 00:39:01.130
By the way...

492
00:39:03.280 --> 00:39:06.340
about the last rule of this Death Note.

493
00:39:07.240 --> 00:39:12.640
"If the owner does not write any name for 13 days"

494
00:39:13.270 --> 00:39:14.160
"the owner shall die."

495
00:39:15.820 --> 00:39:19.860
Considering this rule. the former Kiras have died.

496
00:39:20.350 --> 00:39:22.770
Then Light. who was under surveillance for 18 days?

497
00:39:22.830 --> 00:39:27.560
and Amane. which was 23 days. are completely innocent.

498
00:39:27.760 --> 00:39:28.670
Shinigami!

499
00:39:30.400 --> 00:39:34.130
Are all the rules on this notebook true?

500
00:39:36.460 --> 00:39:38.370
Yes. they are!

501
00:39:42.020 --> 00:39:44.470
I got it. Light and Misa are free now.

502
00:39:46.940 --> 00:39:49.360
Light. call your mother and go home.

503
00:39:49.530 --> 00:39:50.270
Dad!

504
00:39:50.700 --> 00:39:53.460
I'd like to stay here and continue working...

505
00:39:54.390 --> 00:39:55.400
I think I have to.

506
00:39:55.400 --> 00:39:56.410
Light..

507
00:39:57.340 --> 00:39:58.070
Ryuzaki!

508
00:39:59.300 --> 00:40:00.740
You need me. don't you?

509
00:40:02.250 --> 00:40:06.660
I got it.
Light. stay here and help us.

510
00:40:07.500 --> 00:40:09.990
This looks like a common notebook.

511
00:40:10.580 --> 00:40:13.140
I can't believe this thing can kill people.

512
00:40:14.070 --> 00:40:14.960
What?

513
00:40:15.010 --> 00:40:17.010
Why don't you come with me?

514
00:40:17.260 --> 00:40:18.690
You can come whenever you want.

515
00:40:19.140 --> 00:40:20.660
Ryuzaki will allow us

516
00:40:20.940 --> 00:40:22.470
to just talk at the entrance.

517
00:40:23.690 --> 00:40:25.000
Right. I'll come see you everyday!

518
00:40:25.530 --> 00:40:26.420
Be prepared!

519
00:40:33.460 --> 00:40:34.160
Misa...

520
00:40:34.860 --> 00:40:35.900
Listen quietly...

521
00:40:39.220 --> 00:40:40.600
Will you do me a favor?

522
00:40:43.170 --> 00:40:43.890
What is it?

523
00:40:57.460 --> 00:40:58.710
It's here!

524
00:41:38.950 --> 00:41:40.980
Light is Kira...

525
00:41:43.250 --> 00:41:44.510
He's my God!

526
00:41:48.370 --> 00:41:49.210
So happy!

527
00:41:50.590 --> 00:41:52.430
My Light is Kira...!

528
00:41:55.250 --> 00:41:58.230
I'm back at last!

529
00:42:00.040 --> 00:42:00.800
Ryuk!

530
00:42:02.630 --> 00:42:03.830
Why are you here?

531
00:42:04.890 --> 00:42:06.870
That Death Note is mine...

532
00:42:07.840 --> 00:42:09.750
So this time I'll follow you.

533
00:42:11.240 --> 00:42:13.650
Don't worry. your memory won't be gone

534
00:42:14.290 --> 00:42:17.840
if you become the owner of this Note.

535
00:42:20.290 --> 00:42:21.490
Okay. I'll be the owner.

536
00:42:23.680 --> 00:42:24.390
Oh. I almost forgot!

537
00:42:29.530 --> 00:42:29.850
Here!

538
00:42:30.380 --> 00:42:31.320
A gift from Light!

539
00:42:33.270 --> 00:42:34.400
App... Apple!

540
00:42:34.790 --> 00:42:37.400
Oh Light!
He's more generous than he looks!

541
00:42:40.520 --> 00:42:41.370
"Dear Misa."

542
00:42:42.440 --> 00:42:46.960
"When you read this letter. you must've remembered everything."

543
00:42:48.470 --> 00:42:50.470
"To create an ideal world together."

544
00:42:51.420 --> 00:42:53.760
"you must resume punishing instead of me."

545
00:42:55.720 --> 00:42:56.540
"And one more thing."

546
00:42:56.970 --> 00:43:01.700
"Do you remember the guy named Ryuzaki I introduced you at my college?"

547
00:43:02.770 --> 00:43:05.470
"He's our enemy. L!"

548
00:43:07.180 --> 00:43:08.190
That guy is L?

549
00:43:09.060 --> 00:43:13.510
"You must've seen his real name with your Shinigami's eyes."

550
00:43:14.560 --> 00:43:16.260
"Write down the name on the Death Note"

551
00:43:17.040 --> 00:43:18.630
"and eliminate L."

552
00:43:22.900 --> 00:43:24.530
Elminate L...

553
00:43:37.610 --> 00:43:39.170
Damn it!

554
00:43:40.280 --> 00:43:41.940
I can't remember it!

555
00:43:43.810 --> 00:43:48.140
I saw names of hundreds of people everyday.

556
00:43:49.500 --> 00:43:53.530
Once you discard the ownership. you lose the ability of "the eyes".

557
00:43:54.150 --> 00:43:56.220
I'm sorry. Misa.

558
00:43:59.660 --> 00:44:00.680
Ryuk!

559
00:44:02.890 --> 00:44:04.530
Make the eye-deal again.

560
00:44:04.770 --> 00:44:06.170
Are you sure?

561
00:44:07.100 --> 00:44:09.390
You've already lost half of your lifespan.

562
00:44:09.890 --> 00:44:12.030
You'll lose half again!

563
00:44:12.410 --> 00:44:14.310
I know!

564
00:44:15.670 --> 00:44:18.690
I don't want to lose my face!

565
00:44:19.180 --> 00:44:20.050
Face....

566
00:44:21.030 --> 00:44:22.180
but you have the face.

567
00:44:23.370 --> 00:44:25.160
Don't take it literally!

568
00:44:26.770 --> 00:44:29.240
Well. I don't really understand the human mind...

569
00:44:29.710 --> 00:44:32.000
You want the Shinigami's eyes.

570
00:44:36.630 --> 00:44:38.510
I have to obey Light...

571
00:44:49.180 --> 00:44:51.140
Just one week after Takada's death...

572
00:44:53.280 --> 00:44:55.020
A new Kira has appeared!

573
00:44:56.000 --> 00:44:57.470
Criminals are being killed again.

574
00:44:57.880 --> 00:45:01.110
It means there are more notebooks.

575
00:45:02.270 --> 00:45:04.040
Just after

576
00:45:04.430 --> 00:45:06.370
Amane Misa was freed.

577
00:45:07.260 --> 00:45:08.360
Ryuzaki!

578
00:45:08.600 --> 00:45:09.790
Don't give me that again!

579
00:45:09.980 --> 00:45:12.520
Don't you remember the 13 day rule?

580
00:45:13.100 --> 00:45:14.030
Mr. Yagami!

581
00:45:14.930 --> 00:45:15.630
What?

582
00:45:15.970 --> 00:45:19.280
Let's inspect this notebook.

583
00:45:20.930 --> 00:45:24.290
I'll ask FBI and have them provide us with two prisoners from the death row.

584
00:45:25.340 --> 00:45:28.690
We'll make the prisoner A write the name of the prisoner B

585
00:45:28.710 --> 00:45:29.680
to see if B will die.

586
00:45:31.180 --> 00:45:36.080
Then we'll leave A away from the Note for 13 days to see if he will die.

587
00:45:36.580 --> 00:45:40.460
I can't believe you treat human lives like bugs!

588
00:45:41.550 --> 00:45:42.990
It can't be helped.

589
00:45:43.790 --> 00:45:46.250
It's to protect thousands of people's lives.

590
00:45:46.440 --> 00:45:47.640
Isn't there any other way?

591
00:46:08.290 --> 00:46:09.230
Today. again!

592
00:46:09.480 --> 00:46:11.560
A numerous number of criminals are killed.

593
00:46:17.570 --> 00:46:18.200
Ryuzaki!

594
00:46:18.980 --> 00:46:21.470
You may be right to stop Kira from killing people.

595
00:46:22.410 --> 00:46:25.310
I'll take responsibility for the experiment.

596
00:46:25.740 --> 00:46:27.100
I'll supervise.

597
00:46:28.130 --> 00:46:29.040
Dad...

598
00:46:29.880 --> 00:46:32.100
Thank you for understanding!

599
00:46:32.520 --> 00:46:34.240
I'll go to the States.

600
00:46:34.460 --> 00:46:35.820
Are you going alone?

601
00:46:36.730 --> 00:46:38.300
Let me go with you!

602
00:46:38.860 --> 00:46:39.390
No. you can't!

603
00:46:40.190 --> 00:46:42.850
Stay here with Ryuzaki and wait until I contact you.

604
00:46:44.430 --> 00:46:45.250
I'll be fine.

605
00:46:46.190 --> 00:46:48.750
Others will come with me. no need to worry.

606
00:46:49.090 --> 00:46:50.400
Wait. am I worrying?

607
00:46:50.930 --> 00:46:52.550
I am good at shooting

608
00:46:52.730 --> 00:46:53.650
How about here?

609
00:46:53.770 --> 00:46:54.980
Yes. you are worrying.

610
00:47:00.770 --> 00:47:04.720
First. go to the Tokyo Bay heliport by car.

611
00:47:06.170 --> 00:47:12.180
Then fly to the Yokota Camp. The US army will carry you by plane to Washington D.C.

612
00:47:13.160 --> 00:47:14.960
Watari has arranged everything.

613
00:47:15.360 --> 00:47:16.080
I got it!

614
00:47:16.530 --> 00:47:17.680
See you later!

615
00:47:46.510 --> 00:47:48.320
Now. we're all alone.

616
00:47:49.550 --> 00:47:51.020
What are you thinking about?

617
00:47:52.480 --> 00:47:53.350
Right now...

618
00:47:53.990 --> 00:47:56.590
Watari is coming here. Amane!

619
00:47:57.970 --> 00:47:59.590
It was your plan!

620
00:48:00.790 --> 00:48:01.730
Why Misa?

621
00:48:02.850 --> 00:48:07.780
For some reason. the 13 day rule didn't work for Amane

622
00:48:08.580 --> 00:48:10.670
Amane is the Second Kira...

623
00:48:11.380 --> 00:48:13.970
And she has another Death Note.

624
00:48:14.130 --> 00:48:15.850
This is what I'm thinking about.

625
00:48:16.750 --> 00:48:22.750
Then why didn't she write your name when she was freed?

626
00:48:22.910 --> 00:48:27.460
Probably. she forgot my name she saw at the college

627
00:48:27.700 --> 00:48:29.750
while she was restrained.

628
00:48:31.530 --> 00:48:33.860
Forgetting things is a girl's nature.

629
00:48:37.090 --> 00:48:38.460
I am going to

630
00:48:38.930 --> 00:48:41.040
show my face to Amane.

631
00:48:43.110 --> 00:48:44.050
What?

632
00:48:45.050 --> 00:48:46.300
If you do that. she'll...

633
00:48:46.890 --> 00:48:49.090
Yes. she'll definitely write my name..

634
00:48:49.110 --> 00:48:51.280
We can catch her when she's done it.

635
00:48:51.720 --> 00:48:55.410
Let's get her Note!

636
00:48:56.710 --> 00:48:58.470
We never know when and where she'll write it.

637
00:48:58.510 --> 00:49:02.370
There are millions of cameras in this building.

638
00:49:02.450 --> 00:49:04.140
What if she didn't bring the Note?

639
00:49:04.190 --> 00:49:06.370
She'll definitely bring it. This is a huge chance

640
00:49:07.090 --> 00:49:08.490
to kill me.

641
00:49:12.490 --> 00:49:13.500
All right!

642
00:49:14.040 --> 00:49:16.140
Then we'll catch her. and restrain her again

643
00:49:16.300 --> 00:49:18.160
until she tells us about the First Kira.

644
00:49:18.430 --> 00:49:19.620
Is that alright?

645
00:49:20.570 --> 00:49:22.360
We can definitely make her confess

646
00:49:22.840 --> 00:49:24.250
as we have the evidence.

647
00:49:24.670 --> 00:49:27.540
You shut out the crew to do this. didn't you?

648
00:49:28.530 --> 00:49:30.250
If she gets tied like that again

649
00:49:30.930 --> 00:49:33.150
she may die this time.

650
00:49:34.050 --> 00:49:36.180
I know. I feel sorry. but it can't be helped...

651
00:49:46.820 --> 00:49:48.330
What's the matter. Shinigami?

652
00:50:01.090 --> 00:50:03.620
Ryuzaki asked me to come.

653
00:50:03.860 --> 00:50:07.480
Does it mean he doesn't suspect me as Kira anymore?

654
00:50:07.770 --> 00:50:09.490
Of course he doesn't!

655
00:50:23.700 --> 00:50:24.470
But if...

656
00:50:25.310 --> 00:50:27.840
I couldn't save your life...

657
00:50:28.630 --> 00:50:30.980
...If my heart stops...

658
00:50:31.410 --> 00:50:33.860
this sensor will automatically alert Mr. Yagami.

659
00:50:34.570 --> 00:50:36.950
I've asked him to burn the Death Note

660
00:50:37.450 --> 00:50:39.980
to never be used again.

661
00:50:45.130 --> 00:50:47.690
Misa's lifespan has been shortened again.

662
00:50:49.700 --> 00:50:50.560
Lifespan?

663
00:50:51.200 --> 00:50:52.140
What do you mean?

664
00:50:52.190 --> 00:50:53.230
Ryuzaki

665
00:50:54.510 --> 00:50:57.020
If you risk your life I'm prepared too!

666
00:50:58.080 --> 00:50:58.950
Let's catch Amane Misa

667
00:50:59.920 --> 00:51:01.910
...the Second Kira in the act!

668
00:51:08.130 --> 00:51:08.730
Here she comes!

669
00:51:31.960 --> 00:51:33.010
Yagami Light....

670
00:51:34.280 --> 00:51:36.790
You've known that this would happen.

671
00:51:37.990 --> 00:51:42.460
Since I told you that if a Shinigami extends the lifespan of a human

672
00:51:42.510 --> 00:51:43.710
the Shinigami will die.

673
00:51:46.900 --> 00:51:48.890
You drove her into a corner

674
00:51:49.000 --> 00:51:50.410
to make me save her.

675
00:51:51.210 --> 00:51:53.840
It will extend her life

676
00:51:54.010 --> 00:51:55.730
and I will die instead.

677
00:51:56.490 --> 00:52:00.160
That's been your plan from that day.

678
00:52:01.200 --> 00:52:03.850
You'll succeed in killing a Shinigami!

679
00:52:04.820 --> 00:52:07.380
You are the true devil!

680
00:52:09.210 --> 00:52:12.380
But still. Misa loves you.

681
00:52:14.060 --> 00:52:15.670
Yagami Light!

682
00:52:16.200 --> 00:52:19.370
I'll never let you use my Note!

683
00:52:20.690 --> 00:52:21.400
Misa...

684
00:52:22.610 --> 00:52:23.940
Even if a short while...

685
00:52:24.260 --> 00:52:26.380
be happy...

686
00:52:41.960 --> 00:52:42.890
Watari!

687
00:52:43.440 --> 00:52:44.790
Checkmate..!

688
00:53:09.150 --> 00:53:10.500
Did you use...

689
00:53:10.570 --> 00:53:11.630
that Shinigami...?

690
00:53:14.040 --> 00:53:16.560
Remu has a gentle heart.

691
00:53:18.790 --> 00:53:20.330
Yagami Light...

692
00:53:23.460 --> 00:53:24.330
I knew it...

693
00:53:24.510 --> 00:53:25.720
You are Kira.

694
00:53:26.060 --> 00:53:28.190
I wanted to know your name.

695
00:53:30.130 --> 00:53:30.920
Loser!

696
00:53:33.200 --> 00:53:34.460
I am

697
00:53:36.610 --> 00:53:37.520
not a...

698
00:53:46.580 --> 00:53:48.610
Goodbye. L.

699
00:53:49.860 --> 00:53:52.960
You were the best rival

700
00:53:53.420 --> 00:53:55.320
of me. Kira. the God of the new world.

701
00:53:56.400 --> 00:53:58.170
If I had made even a single mistake

702
00:53:58.730 --> 00:54:00.970
I might be dead too.

703
00:54:02.500 --> 00:54:04.990
It was a high risk to release Misa

704
00:54:05.900 --> 00:54:11.110
and let her use the Death Note in my place.

705
00:54:13.340 --> 00:54:16.890
Keep watching me achieving the revolution.

706
00:54:18.400 --> 00:54:21.150
Farewell. L.

707
00:54:23.250 --> 00:54:24.430
I see...

708
00:54:27.590 --> 00:54:29.690
She burnt the Note with her.

709
00:54:34.470 --> 00:54:35.260
Light!

710
00:54:35.470 --> 00:54:36.280
You made it!

711
00:54:36.300 --> 00:54:37.380
Misa. where's the Note?

712
00:54:43.720 --> 00:54:45.670
So. you killed L!

713
00:54:45.780 --> 00:54:47.790
Ryuk! How have you been?

714
00:54:48.000 --> 00:54:49.950
I won. L is dead.

715
00:54:50.230 --> 00:54:51.800
But I still have a job...

716
00:54:57.040 --> 00:54:59.340
"Yagami Soichiro"

717
00:55:02.710 --> 00:55:04.310
"Heart attack"

718
00:55:05.960 --> 00:55:07.980
That's your own father's name. Light!

719
00:55:08.600 --> 00:55:10.060
To create the new world...

720
00:55:11.750 --> 00:55:12.500
But...

721
00:55:15.680 --> 00:55:17.190
He's your father!

722
00:55:17.900 --> 00:55:18.990
Why!

723
00:55:19.120 --> 00:55:20.740
Just shut up!

724
00:55:21.610 --> 00:55:23.320
No matter how much you love something.

725
00:55:24.040 --> 00:55:26.140
there's a time you have make sacrifices.

726
00:55:27.790 --> 00:55:29.690
I cannot be what I used to be.

727
00:55:34.640 --> 00:55:39.850
"Comes back with the Death Note. gives it to Light and dies"

728
00:56:11.800 --> 00:56:12.570
Dad...

729
00:56:22.390 --> 00:56:24.030
Give the Death Note back to me.

730
00:56:28.190 --> 00:56:29.060
Dad!

731
00:56:30.950 --> 00:56:32.930
Since we were young

732
00:56:34.000 --> 00:56:35.730
you didnt't forgive even the most insignificant injustice

733
00:56:36.650 --> 00:56:38.200
and tried to be our model father.

734
00:56:39.480 --> 00:56:41.760
I respect you so much!

735
00:56:43.560 --> 00:56:45.190
So I'm sure you'll understand

736
00:56:46.610 --> 00:56:48.380
what I'm going to do.

737
00:56:49.990 --> 00:56:51.320
What I will achieve.

738
00:56:55.540 --> 00:56:56.180
Dad...

739
00:57:01.200 --> 00:57:02.000
I'm sorry!

740
00:57:03.470 --> 00:57:04.220
It's your time...

741
00:57:16.980 --> 00:57:17.970
Where's the Death Note?

742
00:57:18.460 --> 00:57:19.090
Light!

743
00:57:20.940 --> 00:57:22.360
I saw everything!

744
00:57:26.930 --> 00:57:28.330
I watched you through the cameras

745
00:57:29.780 --> 00:57:31.330
and I heard your voice.

746
00:57:32.130 --> 00:57:32.920
What?

747
00:57:43.630 --> 00:57:44.960
Light!

748
00:57:46.090 --> 00:57:46.990
Light!

749
00:57:48.680 --> 00:57:49.500
You're...

750
00:57:50.930 --> 00:57:51.980
under arrest!

751
00:57:55.650 --> 00:57:57.000
Light.

752
00:57:58.930 --> 00:58:00.590
I'm so sad...

753
00:58:00.770 --> 00:58:02.020
we couldn't be friends.

754
00:58:05.480 --> 00:58:06.620
Ryuzaki?!

755
00:58:09.480 --> 00:58:10.510
You...

756
00:58:12.080 --> 00:58:12.960
Why?

757
00:58:19.670 --> 00:58:21.300
A fake notebook!

758
00:58:22.930 --> 00:58:24.350
Misa. you betrayed me!

759
00:58:25.700 --> 00:58:27.020
No. I didn't!

760
00:58:28.330 --> 00:58:30.590
How can I betray you?

761
00:58:32.280 --> 00:58:35.070
No matter how evil you are

762
00:58:36.570 --> 00:58:38.170
I love you!

763
00:58:41.210 --> 00:58:43.920
She didn't betray you.

764
00:58:45.540 --> 00:58:48.360
It was unexpected that the Shinigami would act that way.

765
00:58:51.240 --> 00:58:52.760
This is the real one

766
00:58:53.310 --> 00:58:55.530
Amane Misa digged out.

767
00:58:57.700 --> 00:58:59.090
And this...

768
00:59:00.240 --> 00:59:03.410
is my real name. which you wanted to know.

769
00:59:07.060 --> 00:59:10.630
You can't change what is written in the Death Note

770
00:59:11.500 --> 00:59:14.370
which means you won't die until the day that was written first.

771
00:59:15.560 --> 00:59:18.840
I'll die in 20 days

772
00:59:19.690 --> 00:59:21.580
so you can't kill me now.

773
00:59:22.900 --> 00:59:24.280
When did you switch them?

774
00:59:25.380 --> 00:59:27.870
The criminals I punished died as planned.

775
00:59:28.860 --> 00:59:30.500
Yes. on the first day.

776
00:59:31.270 --> 00:59:35.290
Then I concluded that you are the Second Kira.

777
00:59:36.160 --> 00:59:38.630
The 13 day rule is also false.

778
00:59:39.080 --> 00:59:41.980
From the second day. Watari switched it into the fake one.

779
00:59:42.830 --> 00:59:44.790
We were watching it

780
00:59:45.560 --> 00:59:48.240
and gave you false information

781
00:59:48.800 --> 00:59:52.610
as if the criminals were killed by Kira.

782
00:59:53.130 --> 00:59:54.770
The biggest goal was. Light.

783
00:59:55.480 --> 00:59:58.350
to confirm that you're Kira.

784
00:59:59.540 --> 01:00:01.000
You're a smart boy!

785
01:00:01.450 --> 01:00:03.270
You didn't give me any clue...

786
01:00:03.480 --> 01:00:04.570
So I decided

787
01:00:06.560 --> 01:00:08.670
to give up my own life.

788
01:00:09.060 --> 01:00:13.060
This plan couldn't succeed without Mr. Yagami's cooperation.

789
01:00:13.960 --> 01:00:16.900
He is a very sincere person. At first he refused to do it.

790
01:00:17.430 --> 01:00:19.840
but when I showed him my name written in the Note

791
01:00:20.400 --> 01:00:22.620
I think he understood that I was serious.

792
01:00:23.060 --> 01:00:25.120
Then he finally agreed

793
01:00:26.070 --> 01:00:28.100
to cooperate with my plan.

794
01:00:30.170 --> 01:00:31.190
He said

795
01:00:32.150 --> 01:00:33.480
that you're not Kira.

796
01:00:34.320 --> 01:00:36.140
He would believe so

797
01:00:36.690 --> 01:00:38.040
until the last moment.

798
01:00:39.330 --> 01:00:41.220
The cars didn't go to the heliport

799
01:00:41.720 --> 01:00:43.570
and everyone was watching

800
01:00:44.080 --> 01:00:46.110
what was happening here.

801
01:01:00.420 --> 01:01:01.700
The saddest thing is

802
01:01:02.720 --> 01:01:03.480
Watari's death.

803
01:01:04.890 --> 01:01:08.200
I couldn't predict that the Shinigami would write his name.

804
01:01:10.040 --> 01:01:11.900
That was my last mistake.

805
01:01:12.790 --> 01:01:13.790
Light!

806
01:01:14.400 --> 01:01:16.000
I will understand

807
01:01:16.690 --> 01:01:19.270
what you are going to do.

808
01:01:19.380 --> 01:01:20.440
You said so.

809
01:01:21.690 --> 01:01:22.580
I'm sorry!

810
01:01:23.390 --> 01:01:24.580
I cannot understand at all.

811
01:01:24.780 --> 01:01:26.400
This isn't justice at all!

812
01:01:31.060 --> 01:01:32.870
Before I got the Death Note

813
01:01:34.740 --> 01:01:38.270
the world was dead. with tons of criminals that current laws can't punish!

814
01:01:40.420 --> 01:01:42.110
It was so unreasonable!

815
01:01:43.660 --> 01:01:44.810
You know what happened

816
01:01:45.730 --> 01:01:48.580
After Kira appeared. the crime rate was decreased by 70%.

817
01:01:50.340 --> 01:01:52.210
Isn't that what you want?

818
01:01:53.730 --> 01:01:55.740
...To live in such a peaceful world?

819
01:02:08.300 --> 01:02:10.400
Light!

820
01:02:15.990 --> 01:02:17.860
A sheet of the Death Note...

821
01:02:17.980 --> 01:02:19.520
I knew you had it.

822
01:02:20.270 --> 01:02:21.970
You killed Takada with that.

823
01:02:24.020 --> 01:02:25.210
At last.

824
01:02:25.660 --> 01:02:26.770
I found the last piece.

825
01:02:49.750 --> 01:02:51.890
You're right. I'm Kira.

826
01:02:53.660 --> 01:02:55.670
I'm the God of the new world.

827
01:02:56.730 --> 01:02:57.720
No. you're not!

828
01:02:58.400 --> 01:03:00.410
You are just a murderer.

829
01:03:01.400 --> 01:03:03.010
